        {
            "title": "獵金•遊戲｜劉德華自爆肝差滴酒不沾 曾被信任的人出賣選擇原諒",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d29918f7d97f2f48915dfd3fbe8d1a2f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250509/_2025050920095268034.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>由邱禮濤執導兼編劇，劉德華、歐豪與倪妮主演的電影《獵金•遊戲》，以股票市場為背景。扮演股票分析師的華仔稱，幸好曾拍《東方華爾街》，對股票有些瞭解，而這次談及香港股市，名詞專業，要牢記，之前未試過像這次般用心做筆記，像默書，他說：「呢次好似做咗文人，好似李白。」撰文：鄺芷瑩、攝影：譚志光；劉德華服裝︰Prada、配飾︰Boucheron、眼鏡︰Puyi Optical、造型︰Queenie Yu\n\n</p><h2>劉德華拍警世故事便宜莫貪</h2>\n<p>提到一頭白髮造型，華仔說沒有偶包，能夠呈現穩重感；同時稱兩年前沒有白頭髮，之後才要染髮。談到演出該片後，會否在投資上更有眼光？華仔否認，發覺投資永遠沒有穩陣，指保本投資大多買「磚頭」。提到戲中被徒弟背叛，問到現實中可有遇到？他坦言有，最嬲是被信任的人出賣，不開心了幾年，就去改變心態，不計較，選擇原諒、寬恕時，運氣也變好了。談到跟倪妮的談情戲，華仔大爆對方飲酒投入角色，「我就滴酒不沾，飲一滴都眼瞓！」所以一班人飲酒時都不想他在場，清醒的他會記下眾人醉態，「我都想飲得，但身體唔得，個肝唔好。」\n\n</p>\n<p>邱禮濤指這次拍攝股票題材電影，跟市民息息相關，指數是經濟寒暑表。擅長拍爆破戲的他轉戰文戲，也不覺容易，需要做許多資料搜集，股票資訊不能錯。問他是否經常「損手」而開拍這個警世故事？他笑言投資獲得正數，要瞭解該公司背景先會買股票，若然只知股票號碼，買了兩日就要「離場」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239919/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"華仔自爆曾經被信任的人出賣，他才發覺嬲是於事無補。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ae3f6debf6d74e0c3ae3d47ba8efb2bb/2025-05/01_KK__3159.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        華仔自爆曾經被信任的人出賣，他才發覺嬲是於事無補。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239920/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"華仔與邱禮濤多次合作，這次以文戲為主。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f9f202513e57d86b41a045d7f1dab43c/2025-05/02_KK__3133.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        華仔與邱禮濤多次合作，這次以文戲為主。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239921/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"華仔拍呢齣戲做咗好多note。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ccc05ed39a3d014c68aea60133c3ec9d/2025-05/03_KK__3112.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        華仔拍呢齣戲做咗好多note。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239923/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"兩人多次合作，包括《掃毒2天地對決》、《拆彈專家》系列、《莫斯科行動》等。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/96fe840f00ec306d3c1068cb69916370/2025-05/KK__3098.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        兩人多次合作，包括《掃毒2天地對決》、《拆彈專家》系列、《莫斯科行動》等。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239924/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉德華今次呢套戲有警世味。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/380a77512646c3f443c6d4d1526b2518/2025-05/KK__3103.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉德華今次呢套戲有警世味。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239930/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉德華話近年有白頭髮，肝又麻麻。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5026baf8cf6d17aeec4d207110661317/2025-05/KK__3126.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉德華話近年有白頭髮，肝又麻麻。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239931/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"導演話拍文戲都好難，資料不能出錯。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e68e49751ea7b0e1b1261b1855ecba0a/2025-05/KK__3127.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        導演話拍文戲都好難，資料不能出錯。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239934/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"華仔在《獵金•遊戲》扮演股票分析師，運籌帷幄。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4faa91f4c2e39544a0f819315a425bd4/2025-05/1_.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        華仔在《獵金•遊戲》扮演股票分析師，運籌帷幄。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239935/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"華仔一頭白髮的霸氣造型，原來是邱禮濤的意思。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/331f0a3fe3fed57f636dc0772437645f/2025-05/174679167130769.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        華仔一頭白髮的霸氣造型，原來是邱禮濤的意思。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239936/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"《獵金•遊戲》以金融騙局為背景，踢爆陰謀。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5f7b216c4396db40efb3d189518c1712/2025-05/174679167116919.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《獵金•遊戲》以金融騙局為背景，踢爆陰謀。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
